ğŸ“Œ Total Revenue: $1M revenue from bookings

ğŸ“Œ Total Room Nights: 8,000 total room nights stayed

ğŸ“Œ Average Room Rate (ARR): $148.4 per night

ğŸ“ˆ Bookings Over Time: Daily booking trends via line chart

ğŸ“Š Bookings by Day of Week: Bar chart to analyze weekday vs weekend demand

